editorialNotes.standard: Few things are more relaxing than settling down with a good colouring book—at least, until the kid we borrowed it from asks for it back. Pigment unleashes our grown-up creative energy with a surprisingly deep array of artist’s tools and tweaks. It even lets us automatically colour within the lines, giving our productions a sheen of perfection. We expect a call from the gallery any day now.

Open this Apple Design Award winner and start colouring. In moments, all your stresses just kinda wash away, right? That’s the nice side effect of this tremendous colouring app. It’s packed with creativity-enhancing tools—spray paint, customized colour palettes, and a huge assortment of intuitive features. Our favourite pictures switch from colouring between the lines to going rogue.
editorialNotes.short: Relax with colouring and immerse yourself in beautiful art.
